                {
                    "name": "Assassin Augmentations",
                    "type": "sidebar",
                    "text": "Clockwork assassins can feature a variety of abilities and mechanisms to better complete their assigned tasks. Assassins expecting to face large groups of enemies have integrated weapons that target multiple foes at once. Other assassins have magical integration, allowing them to cast useful spells.\n",
